high_descs: Turn around then turn left and face the desk in front of you.
Take the CD off of the table in front of you.
Move back and face the table in front of you.
Place the CD under the table in front of you.
Turn left then face the desk on your right.
Take the CD off of the desk in front of you.
Move back and face the desk in front of you.
Place the CD under the desk in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the CD under the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and go past and bed and around the book shelf to the front of the desk.
Pick up the CD on the edge of the desk and in front of the keys.
Move over right to the front of the the drawer below the desk.
Place the CD on the shelf below the desk.
Move back left to the front side of the desk with the CD on top.
Pick up the CD on the desk.
Move back right to the front of the drawers.
Place the CD on the shelf below the desk on the right of the first CD
anns.task_desc: Move two CDs to the drawer shelf below the desk.

high_descs: Turn left, and then turn left again taking five steps, turn right and walk past the partition and turn right. Take a few steps then turn left and face the desk.
Pick up the CD that’s closest to the edge on the right.
While holding the CD, turn all the way around.
Put the CD in the open area above the desk drawer on the bottom right of the desk.
Turn left for a step then turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the CD on the desk.
Turn right and spin all the way around.
Put the CD to the right of the CD already in the open area above the desk drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two CDs in the open space above the drawer on the right side of the desk.
